Title: No Vengeance on an Empty Stomach
Description:
Now that we've gotten back to what we aimed to do, we need to have a talk tusk to tusk. That gnoll Frostbite? The one you spoke to?

We've got a history with him.

This may take awhile to explain. You go and get some fish while I talk, pup. We need to feed everyone. They need their strength for what's next.
ObjectivesText: Fish 3 Frozen Tail Darters within Grimtusk's Hideaway.
RewardText:
Now you know what's at stake. 

Time to get moving.

Objectives.Text: Fishing skill learned from Young Quickhands
